{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"06acbb24-9fde-4635-95e9-f256a5f88ebd","content":"There's no workflow file in the current directory, so here's a general guide for the migration:\n\n### Key changes to switch to NuGet Trusted Publishing (OIDC)\n\n**1. Configure NuGet.org** — register your GitHub repo as a trusted publisher:\n- Go to **nuget.org → Manage Packages → your package → Trusted Publishers**\n- Add your GitHub repository, branch/tag pattern, and workflow filename\n\n**2. Update your workflow** — three changes:\n\n```yaml\n# (a) Add OIDC permission at job level\npermissions:\n  id-token: write   # required for OIDC token\n  contents: read\n\n# (b) Replace the dotnet nuget push step:\n- name: Push to NuGet\n  run: dotnet nuget push \"**/*.nupkg\" \\\n    --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n  # No --api-key flag needed!\n\n# (c) Remove any reference to secrets.NUGET_API_KEY\n```\n\n**3. Remove the secret** — once verified, delete `NUGET_API_KEY` from your repo/org secrets.\n\n### Why it works\nGitHub Actions mints a short-lived OIDC token. NuGet.org validates it against the trusted-publisher config (repo, workflow, branch) and authorizes the push — no long-lived secret needed.\n\n### Important notes\n- The `dotnet nuget push` in .NET SDK **8.0.400+** supports OIDC natively. Older SDKs need the `--api-key` replaced with an explicit token exchange step.\n- The workflow **filename** and **environment** (if any) must match what you registered on nuget.org exactly.\n\nWould you like me to create a sample workflow file?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"2bce4f70-65e3-4097-94b7-f33104e6ac69","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"There are no files in the repository. The user is asking a general question about switching from NuGet API key-based publishing to NuGet trusted publishing (OIDC) in GitHub Actions. Let me provide guidance based on my knowledge.","outputTokens":485,"requestId":"FE10:299D5F:1372664:15C4E3B:6A066E89"},"id":"ad420ee6-3398-4213-b48c-a00dc3fbeb41","timestamp":"2026-05-15T00:53:41.935Z","parentId":"1c8c1814-63f2-4c5a-a2f1-4a5b2b0ea28f"}
